16:9 aspect ratio size.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/social-media-image-sizes-youtube.jpg\" alt=\"social media image sizes - youtube banner size example \" width=\"900\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-79903 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/social-media-image-sizes-youtube.jpg 900w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/social-media-image-sizes-youtube-480x202.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@PurCosmetics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>This YouTube channel banner example<\/em><\/a><em> could probably be resized to align with the auto-crop that was applied. <\/em><\/p>\n<div id=\"social-media-image-tools\"><\/div>\n<h2>Tools to help with social media image sizes<\/h2>\n<p>To help you with your editing, check out some of these top social media image and video tools.<\/p>\n<h3><span>Canva<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>When it comes to social media image sizing, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.canva.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Canva<\/a> can be an excellent resource. <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/how-to-use-canva\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Canva is free to use<\/a>, or you can pay for a Canva Pro subscription too. Both come with options for social media templates, free-to-use graphics and photos, as well as plenty of easy-to-navigate editing and cropping tools.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/social-media-image-sizes-canva.jpg\" alt=\"social media image size tools - canva\" width=\"626\" height=\"272\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-79911 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/social-media-image-sizes-canva.jpg 626w, https:\/\/www.